reviewText: Unfortunately, this dvd set did not have the episodes that I wanted, but it is still a great television series. Because they do not list what episodes are on the dvd, I am listing them for anyone who might like this information: There are four episodes: 1. "The Archbishop and Chico (1956), 2. "Grandpa Changes the World (1956), 3. Pit-A-Pit and the Dragon" (1957), 4. The Intruder (1957)
